        "text": "### Original Publication\n\nThe primary literature source recorded for this value is:\n\n> **Author:** Gerold Anderegg\n> **Title:** *\"Critical Survey of Stability Constants of EDTA Complexes\"*\n> **Publisher:** Pergamon Press, Oxford\n> **Year:** **1977**\n> *(SRD-46 shortcut code: 77Aee)*\n\nThis entry is a critically evaluated recommended value compiled by **Gerold Anderegg** and published in **1977**. It draws upon a vast body of experimental work — 49 individual literature references spanning from 1949 to 1998 are linked to this measurement in SRD-46, including early pioneering studies by Schwarzenbach (1949, 1951), Martell and Plumb (1952), and many others.",
